## 1. Introduction

BMI & Health (‚Äúthe app‚Äù) is a simple, offline-first BMI calculator designed to help users calculate and track their Body Mass Index (BMI).
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how the app handles user data.

---

## 2. Data Collection

**BMI & Health does not collect any personal data.**

The app:

* Does **not** require account registration
* Does **not** collect names, email addresses, phone numbers, or identifiers
* Does **not** collect health data beyond BMI values stored locally on your device
* Does **not** collect location data
* Does **not** collect usage analytics

All BMI calculations and history are stored **locally on the user‚Äôs device only**.

---

## 3. Data Storage

Any information entered into the app (such as height, weight, age, and calculated BMI values) is:

* Stored **only on the user‚Äôs device**
* Never transmitted to any server
* Never backed up to the cloud by the app
* Removed if the app is uninstalled or if the user clears the app‚Äôs data

The app uses Android‚Äôs local storage mechanisms to store BMI history for user convenience.

---

## 4. Data Sharing

**BMI & Health does not share any data with third parties.**

The app:

* Does not sell data
* Does not share data
* Does not transmit data to external servers

---

## 5. Third-Party Services

The app does **not** use:

* Advertising services
* Analytics services
* Tracking SDKs

The app may contain **external links** (such as Instagram, GitHub, LinkedIn, X, or a personal website).
When you click these links, you are redirected to external websites, which have their own privacy policies. BMI & Health is not responsible for the privacy practices of those websites.

---

## 6. Children‚Äôs Privacy

BMI & Health is **not designed for children under the age of 13**.
The app does not knowingly collect any personal information from children.

---

## 7. Health Disclaimer

BMI is a general health indicator and **not a medical diagnosis**.
BMI & Health does not provide medical advice and should not replace professional healthcare consultation.

---

